  <div class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p> Communificiency is a platform for crowdfunding energy efficiency for local businesses. Customers are incentivized to contribute to energy efficiency projects by the rewards local businesses offer. Think about us as Kickstarter for energy efficiency.
    </p>

    <h1>Our vision</h1>
    <p>We believe that delivering clean and sustainable energy represents the greatest challenge of our generation. We are frustrated that market failures prevent the most sensible solutions, such as energy efficiency, from gaining necessary investment and adoption. We believe in the power of communities and technology to overcome these market failures. We are building a platform to transform the future of energy finance.  </p>
